On 7/20/03 11:03 AM, "Tom and Thanh" <tom.loan(-at-)rogers.com> wrote:

> One thing I would like to know is will a ball joint pickle fork tool remove
> the drag link from my Pitman arm without damaging the seal or joint? Or what
> is the best tool or method for removing it?

Use a two jaw puller like Bentley shows: it can be torqued up to 80 ft. lbs.
I don't know about yours but mine looks pretty rusty so I'd start with some
penetrating fluid.

